item.title: Unto Thee, Oh Lord
item.description: [verse 1] Unto Thee, Oh Lord Do I lift up my soul, (2) [Chorus] Oh! My God, I trust in Thee, Let me not be ashamed, Let not my enemies triumph over me [verse 2] Show me Thy ways, Thy ways Oh Lord! (2) Teach me Thy paths, Thy paths Oh Lord! (2) Let none that wait, on Thee be ashamed. (2)
